Ishuri rikuru ry'Ubuvuzi n'Ubuzima ni rimwe mumashuri atandatu agize kaminuza y'u Rwanda. Iri shuri ryashyizweho muburyo bwemewe namategeko rikaba ryarashinzwe kuya 15 Ukwakira 2013.<ref>https://schoolsinrwanda.com/listing/college-of-medicine-and-health-sciences-cmhs-ur/</ref> Iri shuri rikuru rizwi kandi ku izina rya UR-CMHS, rikaba rifite uruhare runini mu iterambere ry’imibereho n’ubukungu by’igihugu binyuze mu guhugura abaganga b’inzobere n’inzobere mu buzima. Mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ibi, Ishuri rikuru ryubaka ubushobozi bujyanye niyi mpamvu mu kuyobora gahunda zamahugurwa yubuzima no kongerera ubushobozi, binyuze muri gahunda zikomeye kandi zifite akamaro.<ref>https://cmhs.ur.ac.rw/spip.php?rubrique17#</ref>
